# Boolean Expressions

The condition inside an if statement must evaluate to a boolean value.

Examples

```java
age >= 18
```

```java
marks > 40
```

```java
salary < 50000
```

These expressions return either:

```
true
```

or

```
false
```

---

# Time Complexity

A single if statement performs one condition check.

Time Complexity

```
O(1)
```

