# Important Definitions

## Control Statement

A statement that controls the flow of execution of a program.

---

## if Statement

Executes a block only when the condition is true.

---

## if-else Statement

Executes one block when the condition is true and another block when the condition is false.

---

## else-if Ladder

Checks multiple conditions sequentially until one becomes true.

---

## Nested if

An if statement inside another if statement.

