# Common Interview Mistakes

❌

```java
if(age = 18)
```

Wrong.

---

✅

```java
if(age == 18)
```

Correct.

---

❌

```java
if(10)
```

Compilation Error.

Java requires a boolean expression.

---

❌

Using multiple independent if statements when only one result should be printed.

Use an else-if ladder instead.

